The project API is open to the Public. The API gives current and basic information about the Corona Virus Case (Covid-19) around the World

For more analysis and research using our API, see more details on the API documentation website:
https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/9033557/SzezcrVF 

The World API: 
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=world

Africa:
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=africa

Europe:
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=europe

North America:
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=northamerica

Asia:
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=asia

South America:
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=southamerica

Oceania
https://reisparcovid19.herokuapp.com?continent=oceania
